				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9868460#post-4152556</guid>
				<title>Minor Stylistic Changes</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-9868460/scp-4359#post-4152556</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 13 Feb 2019 20:35:18 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>Reverend Fox</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1893953</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I swapped out the default font for <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/IM+Fell+DW+Pica+SC">IM Fell DW Pica SC</a> in the newspaper clipping.</p> <p>Also, as Monotype Corsiva doesn't work on all devices and is a non-free font, I swapped it out for <a href="https://fonts.google.com/specimen/Permanent+Marker">Permanent Marker</a>.</p> <p>IMHO, both of these changes improve the look massively!</p> <p>Fonts referenced here are from Google Fonts and are available under the <a href="http://scripts.sil.org/cms/scripts/page.php?site_id=nrsi&amp;id=OFL_web">Open Font License</a> and the <a href="http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0">Apache License 2.0</a>, respectively.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
