						 <p>Hi there! This is one skip out of, hopefully, a full series based around a GoI draft I've been working on for, embarrassingly enough, a little over a <em>year</em>.</p> <p>Mining history has <em>always</em> been a deep interest of mine because I live in Nevada's Mine Country, just down the mountain from the Comstock Range (Virginia City).</p> <p>I want to thank <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-scary-name-man" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3369416&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546908450" alt="The Scary Name Man" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3369416)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/the-scary-name-man" >The Scary Name Man</a></span> and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1404533&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546908450" alt="Zyn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1404533)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zyn" >Zyn</a></span> for the forum critiques and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dankaar" ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1790336&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1546908450" alt="dankaar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1790336)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dankaar" >dankaar</a></span> for the PM crit for last looks!</p> <p>Y'all rock<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-168317-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" >1</a></sup>!</p> <div class="footnotes-footer"> <div class="title">Footnotes</div> <div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-168317-1"><a href="javascript:;" >1</a>. Get it? 'Cause it's a mining-based skip! See? <span style="font-size:70%;">~slaps wrist~</span> <span style="font-size:60%;">Bad Fox!</span></div> </div> 
